<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Invitación</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #ffecd2, #fcb69f);
            color: #333;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 50px;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            display: inline-block;
            position: relative;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #ff7e5f;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 20px;
        }
        .button {
            background-color: #ff7e5f;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin: 10px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        .button:hover {
            background-color: #ff6b4e;
        }
        .button-no {
            background-color: #ccc;
            color: #333;
            position: absolute;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin: 10px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        .message {
            display: none;
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #ff7e5f;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
    <script>
        function moveButton() {
            const button = document.getElementById('button-no');
            button.style.top = Math.random() * (window.innerHeight - 50) + 'px';
            button.style.left = Math.random() * (window.innerWidth - 100) + 'px';
        }

        function showMessage() {
            const message = document.getElementById('message');
            message.style.display = 'block';
        }
    </script>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>¡Hola!</h1>
        <p>Me gustaría invitarte a salir este jueves.</p>
        <p>¿Te gustaría acompañarme en un día bonito?</p>
        <button class="button" onclick="showMessage()">¡Sí, me encantaría!</button>
        <button id="button-no" class="button-no" onmouseover="moveButton()">No, gracias</button>
        <div id="message" class="message">
            <p>¡Yo sabía que ibas a aceptar! ❤️</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
